# Techno-Economic Analysis of Deep Decarbonization Pathways for the South Korean Petrochemical Industry

**Authors:** [Your Name], [Co-authors]
**Affiliation:** PLANiT, Seoul, South Korea
**Corresponding Author:** [Email]  
